  "detailed_description": "<strong>Ragdoll Destroyer</strong> is a physics-based game where your goal is to destroy a ragdoll character! Customize the ragdoll to your liking, select a room, and let the fun begin. Doing more damage to the ragdoll will help you unlock more tools in your toolbox. Tools include a crusher, cannon, rocket launcher, spikes, and more. <br><br>Players have lots of customization options. They can adjust the player's size, color, clothing, gender, and even face. Players can load custom images to use as character faces.<br><br>Will you blow your ragdoll up? Light him on fire? Toss him into traffic? <strong>The choice is yours.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Ragdoll Destroyer</strong> is a physics-based game where your goal is to destroy a ragdoll character! Customize the ragdoll to your liking, select a room, and let the fun begin. Doing more damage to the ragdoll will help you unlock more tools in your toolbox. Tools include a crusher, cannon, rocket launcher, spikes, and more. <br><br>Players have lots of customization options. They can adjust the player's size, color, clothing, gender, and even face. Players can load custom images to use as character faces.<br><br>Will you blow your ragdoll up? Light him on fire? Toss him into traffic? <strong>The choice is yours.</strong>",
